      "title": "National fuel license is being tested in all 25 districts today",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "If the National Fuel License is not valid, Q.R. Mr. Kanchana Wijesekera, the Minister of Electricity and Energy, said that the method of issuing fuel under the code system will be tested today in a way that covers all the 25 districts of the island. Thus, this system is going to be tested in 25 selected filling stations of 25 districts."
